FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,FSpeaking at a White House press
OL,8,Fbriefing, Vance said Western countries
OL,9,Fhad become too reliant on "cheap
OL,10,Flabour" and argued that governments
OL,11,Fshould prioritise higher wages and
OL,12,Finvestment in domestic workers instead.
OL,14,FThe prime minister has accused the
OL,15,FUnite the Kingdom organisers of
OL,16,F"peddling hatred and division, plain
OL,17,Fand simple".
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@GO]xD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
