OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,FThe government blocked 11 foreign
OL,8,Fnationals described by Keir Starmer as
OL,9,F"far-right agitators" from entering
OL,10,Fthe UK ahead of the march.
OL,12,FThe Unite the Kingdom protest and a
OL,13,Fsimultaneous pro-Palestine rally
OL,14,Fsparked a huge #4.5 million police
OL,15,Foperation and there were dozens of
OL,16,Farrests.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
