OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,FAbout 60,000 people were estimated to
OL,8,Fhave joined the Unite the Kingdom
OL,9,Fmarch in the capital, and between
OL,10,F15,000 and 20,000 attended the Nakba
OL,11,FDay rally in support of Palestine, Met
OL,12,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
