OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,FOverall, there were 43 arrests on the
OL,8,Fday, with 20 linked to the Unite the
OL,9,FKingdom protest and 12 with the Nakba
OL,10,Fprotest, the force said. There were 11
OL,11,Farrests of hate crime-related
OL,12,Foffences, nine of which were
OL,13,Faffiliated with the Unite the Kingdom
OL,14,Fmarch and two with the pro-Palestine
OL,15,Fevent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
