PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,FAsked about the rally by a US
OL,8,Freporter, Vance said: "What we believe
OL,9,Fin this White House is what we need
OL,10,Fmore and more of is high wages for
OL,11,FAmerican workers and investing in our
OL,12,Fown people.
OL,14,F"What you see all over the West, and
OL,15,Fit's kind of crazy, is this idea that
OL,16,Fthe way to generate prosperity is to
OL,17,Fbring in millions and millions of
OL,18,Funvetted people and drop them into
OL,19,Fyour neighbourhoods, and we simply
OL,20,Freject that idea.
OL,26,@pD@WOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,F"So, to everybody in the UK who
OL,8,Frejects that idea, I'd encourage them
OL,9,Fto just keep on going."
OL,11,FVance called on Britain to follow the
OL,12,FUnited States in tightening its
OL,13,Fborders.
OL,15,FHe said: "It's OK to want to defend
OL,16,Fyour culture. It's OK to want to live
OL,17,Fin a safe neighbourhood. It's OK to
OL,18,Fwant your job to go to yourself and
OL,19,Fyour neighbours, and not to a stranger
OL,20,Fwho you don't even know.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@WO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,F"It is reasonable for the people in
OL,8,FWestern societies to want to control
OL,9,Fwho comes into their country and who
OL,10,Fdoesn't.
OL,12,F"A lot of people, frankly, a lot of
OL,13,Fpeople in the media, have tried to
OL,14,Fpersuade all of those people that it's
OL,15,Fsomehow racist to want to protect your
OL,16,Fborders, even though very often the
OL,17,Fvery people who are most affected by
OL,18,Flow-wage immigration are lower-income
OL,19,FBlack and Hispanic Americans right
OL,20,Fhere in the United States of America,
OL,21,Fand I guarantee that's true in the UK.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779282676
OL,3,CJD Vance tells UK anti-immigration
OL,4,Cprotesters 'it's OK to defend your
OL,5,Cculture'
OL,7,F"So, we believe in making America
OL,8,Fgreat again. You can't do that unless
OL,9,Fyou protect your borders. I'd
OL,10,Fencourage our friends in the UK to
OL,11,Ffollow the same path."
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
